Inclusion Criteria:

For dose escalation cohorts only:

\- Pathologically confirmed breast cancer with the following features:

* Measurable disease by RECIST 1.1;
* ER and PR ≤ 1% by immunohistochemistry;
* Her-2/neu negative (0 or 1+ by immunohistochemistry OR not-amplified by CAP/ASCO standards);

Inclusion Criteria:

1. Before any trial-related procedures, sign a written informed consent, and be willing and able to follow the planned visits, research treatment, laboratory examination and other test procedures;
